        public Port(HexLocation location,
            EdgeLocation direction,
            int ratio,
            PortType resource)
        Parameters:
        location - Which hex this port is on. This shows the (ocean/non-existent) hex to draw the port on.
        direction - Which edge this port is on.
        ratio - The ratio for trade in (ie, if this is 2, then it's a 2:1 port.
        resource - What type resource this port trades for. If it's omitted, then it's for any resource.
